 02733            string sVal = string.Empty;
 02734            sToval = string.Empty;
 02735            string[] Symbol = new string[] { "^`^" };
 02736             if (ToValue.Split(Symbol, StringSplitOptions.None).Length > 0)
 2737            {
 02738                sToval = ToValue.Split(Symbol, StringSplitOptions.None)[0];
 02739                 sToval = !string.IsNullOrEmpty(sToval) ? GetTermText(sToval, "", "") : string.Empty;
 2740            }
 02741             if (ToValue.Split(Symbol, StringSplitOptions.None).Length > 1)
 2742            {
 02743                sVal = ToValue.Split(Symbol, StringSplitOptions.None)[1];
 2744            }
 02745            return sVal;
 2746        }

 2748        public static string ValueReplace(string sVal)
 2749        {
 02750            string FinalValue = string.Empty;
 02751             if (sVal != null && sVal.Contains('$'))
 2752            {
 02753                String[] sFromSplit = sVal.Split('~');
 2754                //StringBuilder[] s = "Normal";
 02755                int FCount = sFromSplit.Count();
 02756                 for (int i = 0; i < FCount; i++)
 2757                {
 02758                     if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(sFromSplit[i]))
 2759                    {
 02760                        sFromSplit[i] = sFromSplit[i].Insert(sFromSplit[i].Length, ";");
 2761                    }
 02762                    string FstValue = sFromSplit[i];
 2763
 02764                     if (FstValue.Contains('$'))
 2765                    {
 02766                        string[] SplitVal = sFromSplit[i].Split('$');
 02767                        string ReplaceVal = SplitVal[1].Replace('$', ' '); // FromValue.IndexOf("$") >= 0 ? FromValue.Su
 02768                        FinalValue += ";" + GetTermValue(ReplaceVal) + "," + SplitVal[2] + System.Environment.NewLine;
 2769                        //chocksadd
 02770             if (FinalValue.Contains(";"))
 02771                            FinalValue = FinalValue.Remove(FinalValue.LastIndexOf(";"));
 2772            //chocksadd
 2773                    }
 02774                     else if (FstValue.IndexOf('~') == FstValue.Length - 1)
 2775                    {
 02776                        FstValue = FstValue.Replace('~', ' ').Trim();
 02777                        FinalValue += FstValue.Trim();
 2778            //chocksadd
 2779                        //if (FinalValue.Contains(";"))
 2780                        //    FinalValue = FinalValue.Remove(FinalValue.LastIndexOf(";"));
 2781            //chocksadd
 2782                    }
 2783                    else
 2784                    {
 02785                        FstValue = FstValue.Replace('~', '\n');
 2786                        //chocksadd
 02787                         if (FstValue.Contains(";"))
 02788                            FstValue = FstValue.Remove(FstValue.LastIndexOf(";"));
 2789
 02790                        FinalValue += ";" + FstValue.Trim(); //chocksadd
 2791
 2792            //chocksadd
 2793            //FinalValue += FstValue.Trim();
 2794                        //if (FinalValue.Contains(";"))
 2795                        //    FinalValue = FinalValue.Remove(FinalValue.LastIndexOf(";"));
 2796                        //chocksadd
 2797                    }
 2798
 2799                }
 2800            }
 2801            else
 2802            {
 02803                 if (sVal.Contains(";"))
 2804                {
 02805                    sVal = sVal.Remove(sVal.LastIndexOf(";"));
 2806                }
 02807                FinalValue = sVal;
 2808            }
 02809            return FinalValue;
 2810        }

 4307        {
 4308
 4309            //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 4310            //  Change History
 4311            //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 4312            //  Date      Edit    Author            Comment

 4317            public static DateDiff GetDateDiff(DateTime date1, DateTime date2)
 4318            {
 04319                DateDiff objDateDiff = new DateDiff();
 04320                TimeSpan tsAge = date2 - date1;
 04321                bool sticky = true;
 4322                // ensure that date1 <= date2
 04323                 if (date2 < date1)
 4324                {
 04325                    DateTime t = date2;
 04326                    date2 = date1;
 04327                    date1 = t;
 4328                }
 4329                // make a guess at the answer; using 31 means that we'll be close but won't exceed
 4330                //Modified  by jereesh
 4331                // int monthCount = ((date2 - date1).Days / 31);
 04332                int monthCount = date2.Month - date1.Month;
 4333
 4334                // find the maximum number of months that's less than or equal to the second date
 04335                DateTime testDate = DateAddMonths(date1, monthCount, sticky);
 04336                 while (testDate < date2)
 4337                {
 04338                    testDate = DateAddMonths(date1, ++monthCount, sticky);
 4339                }
 4340                // if we've hit the exact date, return the number of months and zero days
 04341                 if (testDate == date2)
 4342                {
 04343                    objDateDiff.Day = 0;
 04344                    objDateDiff.Month = monthCount % 12;
 04345                    objDateDiff.Year = monthCount / 12;
 4346                }
 4347                else
 4348                {
 4349                    // otherwise we exceeded the second date, back up and return the correct values
 04350                    testDate = DateAddMonths(date1, --monthCount, sticky);
 04351                    objDateDiff.Month = monthCount % 12;
 04352                    objDateDiff.Year = monthCount / 12;
 04353                    objDateDiff.Day = (date2 - testDate).Days;
 4354                }
 04355                return objDateDiff;
 4356            }
 4357            public static DateTime DateAddMonths(DateTime startDate, int monthCount, bool sticky)
 4358            {
 4359                //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 4360                //  Change History
 4361                //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 4362                //  Date      Edit    Author            Comment
 4363                //--------------|----------|-------------|-------------------------------------------------
 4364                //01-Sep-2006    [100]    JER      Created
 4365                //-------------+-----+-----+---------------------------------------------------------------
 4366
 04367                DateTime result = startDate.AddMonths(monthCount);
 04368                 if (sticky)
 4369                {
 04370                     if (DateTime.DaysInMonth(startDate.Year, startDate.Month) == startDate.Day)
 4371                    {
 04372                        int resultYear = result.Year;
 04373                        int resultMonth = result.Month;
 04374                        result = new DateTime(resultYear, resultMonth,
 04375                            DateTime.DaysInMonth(resultYear, resultMonth));
 4376                    }
 4377                }
 04378                return result;
 4379            }
 4380        }
